00:41:23.833 --> 00:41:30.767
But it's the red ones, with
their light masses and their

00:41:30.767 --> 00:41:34.033
preference for either bonding
not at all with other

00:41:34.033 --> 00:41:37.900
molecules, or their preference
for bonding with other light

00:41:37.900 --> 00:41:41.767
molecules, that makes them good
candidates for being an

00:41:41.767 --> 00:41:45.300
atmospheric gas.

00:41:45.300 --> 00:41:48.767
In the black circles are
