00:42:06.933 --> 00:42:12.900
And then the way they bond will
make them heavier still.

00:42:12.900 --> 00:42:15.267
And therefore you wouldn't
expect to find them as

00:42:15.267 --> 00:42:17.200
atmospheric gases.

00:42:17.200 --> 00:42:21.600
You'd rather find them in some
more condensed body like the

00:42:21.600 --> 00:42:24.333
