include everything all the

00:42:50.267 --> 00:42:53.067
way from the surface--top of the
atmosphere to the center

00:42:53.067 --> 00:42:56.467
of the planet, there's a
remarkable similarity between

00:42:56.467 --> 00:42:59.867
the compositions of the
different planets.

00:42:59.867 --> 00:43:02.633
For example, in the case of
Jupiter, it probably has all

00:43:02.633 --> 00:43:04.400
